<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Packs et Tarifs - Wendladfan</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; background: #f5f5f5; }
        h1 { color: #1a5f7a; text-align: center; }
        .packs { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; }
        .pack { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; flex: 1; min-width: 250px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .pack h2 { color: #1a5f7a; }
        .pack .price { font-size: 2rem; color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold; }
        .btn { display: block; background: #1a5f7a; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 30px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .wa-btn { background: #25D366; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>📦 Nos Packs et Tarifs</h1>
    <div class="packs">
        <div class="pack">
            <h2>🟢 Pack Starter</h2>
            <p>CV + Lettre simple</p>
            <p>ou Logo simple</p>
            <p class="price">5 000 F</p>
            <a href="/paiement?pack=starter" class="btn">Choisir</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pack">
            <h2>🔵 Pack Pro</h2>
            <p>CV Pro + PowerPoint</p>
            <p>ou Logo + Carte de visite</p>
            <p class="price">25 000 F</p>
            <a href="/paiement?pack=pro" class="btn">Choisir</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pack">
            <h2>🟠 Pack Business</h2>
            <p>Identité complète</p>
            <p>ou Site web + Réseaux</p>
            <p class="price">50 000 F</p>
            <a href="/paiement?pack=business" class="btn">Choisir</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:40px; padding:20px; background:#e8f4f8; border-radius:12px; text-align:center;">
        <h3>💬 Besoin d'un service personnalisé ?</h3>
        <a href="https://wa.me/22652580895" class="btn wa-btn">📱 Contactez-nous sur WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
